hero.hero_overview:
Harley is a killer magician (assassin) who combines mobility and high magic damage. Great for:

Jungle games (jungle);

Middle line (mid lane);

Raids on the enemy line;

Quick elimination of vulnerable heroes (kari, magicians)

hero.hero_strength:
Key features

Mobility: the ability to teleport (Space Escape) allows you to unexpectedly appear and disappear from the battlefield.

Explosive damage: skill combinations deal significant magic damage in a short time.

Reducing enemy protection: the passive skill "Magic Master" reduces the magic defense of enemies for a few seconds.

Control over the enemy: Deadly Magic slows down the enemy and deals damage over time.

Mixed base attack: Harley's basic attacks deal magic damage (+50% physical attack and 60% magic power).

3. Skills (skills)

Passive skill - Magic Master: basic attacks deal magic damage and reduce the magical defense of enemies by 3 seconds.

The first skill is Poker Trick: Harley throws 3-5 waves of cards, inflicting magic damage and increasing the attack speed by 5-10% with each blow (up to 8 times).

The second skill is "Space Escape": teleportation in the selected direction with a speed increase of 30% for 2 seconds. You can return to the starting point in 4 seconds.

Ultimate - Deadly Magic: creates a ring of fire around the enemy, inflicting 200-400 units of magic damage and slowing down by 40% for 1.5 seconds. The ring explodes, indicting additional damage.

4. Strengths

High explosive damage;

Excellent mobility (scape and initiation);

Good control over the enemy;

Quick cleaning of lines and jungles;

Short reload times of skills;

Versatility (suitable for jungle and midlane).

5. Weaknesses

Low survival rate (squashes);

Mana addiction (mana-dependent hero);

The need for accurate aiming with some skills;

Ulta can be blocked by other heroes.
